le-core runs for each incident field considered, the proposed\n  algorithm can effectively solve scattering problems for large and\n  complex objects possibly containing strong refractivity contrasts\n  and discontinuities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 18:32:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Oct 2022 08:16:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-11"}
