 spectra\nand DLU of optimal S-boxes with $4$ bit by Magma. Finally, we investigate the\nDLCT spectra and DLU of some polynomials over $F_{2^n}$, including the inverse,\nGold, Bracken-Leander power functions and all quadratic polynomials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Jul 2019 00:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
